OL,5,G1900 Motorway Cops: Catching Britain's
OL,6,G     Speeders
OL,7,     FAt Grimsby docks, Sergeant Tom
OL,8,     FElvidge pursues teenagers
OL,9,     Fsuspected of trying to steal a
OL,10,     Fmoped. With no time to wait for
OL,11,     Fbackup, a solo Tom chases after
OL,12,     Fthem.
OL,13,G2000 Police Interceptors
OL,14,     FThis episode kicks off with the
OL,15,     Fpursuit of a cloned car. The
OL,16,     Fdriver manages to give Scott the
OL,17,     Fslip by heading the wrong way down
OL,18,     Fa dual carriageway - a recipe for
OL,19,     Fcarnage.
